{
  "stem": "5470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no exchange of what we were doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Certainly not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at the end, when I was already appointed the camp commander of Camp Westerbork in the period of [INAUDIBLE] when the Germans were leaving at that time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no connections even at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got to know even in 1949-- that's when I met other people from other groups.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said we had the intention of taking over Camp Westerbork, but then we got the message that you were going to take over.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's what the first connection, what I actually noticed, that were between our group and another group.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was called [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Pereau. ?] That was some sort of connection, but for the rest, no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were all in separate groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The combination of all these groups were built up after war action, not during the war at all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Certainly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was following that from the beginning on, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's where I got my first contacts, actually, with the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Got to know that they were Jewish people, you could better say that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew quite a number of people but not as Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's where we got more acquainted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were discussing and the friend says when they-- before the time already, there was some connection, but as soon as they were building it up to wear the yellow star, Star of David, and then it became more [INAUDIBLE], because I remember there one Sunday that for the first time that they had to wear those Stars of Davids.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody who would like to show that they were not in agreement what the Germans were doing nipped their hats or greeted them.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
